data.description: Discover contemporary living in this 3-bedroom gem at 307 Masters Avenue, ideally located in the heart of Wylie, Texas. This 1,297 sqft residence boasts a detached workshop with electric, making it perfect for your creative endeavors. Kirby Park is just a stone's throw away, offering a place for the kids to play and swing. Inside, a sleek kitchen with granite countertops beckons culinary enthusiasts, while the covered front porch provides the perfect spot for your morning coffee. Easy access to Highway 78 and downtown Wylie ensures you're well-connected to all the amenities the city has to offer. This beautiful home is waiting for you to make it your own. Foundation work recently completed.
